com.dua3.utility.fx.controls.ProgressView<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of the tasks being tracked
All Implemented Interfaces:
ProgressTracker<T>, javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class ProgressView<T> extends javafx.scene.layout.GridPane implements ProgressTracker<T>
ProgressView is a UI component that displays the progress of tasks in a grid layout. It extends GridPane and implements the ProgressTracker interface.
